       tar cvzf esom-%(version)s.tar.gz *
(4): Move esom-%(version)s.tar.gz to the directory with the SCGid source files (in the EasyBuild sourcepath).
(5): Re-run EasyBuild to install this SCGid easyconfig file.
"""

